bio.openEndedText: I am very passionate about cars. I do this as a hobby and look forward to making your travels safe and comfortable

Full Time Turo Rental Host that focuses on Quality Cars, Exceptional Customer Service and contactless delivery and pickup. As a seasoned Business Traveler I personally understand the need for trusted vehicles and Hosts. I look forward to working with you on your current and future car rental needs. Im always a Text message away with any questions before, during and after your trips. We look forward to serving you and we will treat you like family at all times.

Hey there! 

Thanks for choosing to rent with us on Turo. I'm Rock, and I'll be your host during your trip. 

I want to make sure you have an amazing experience, so let me tell you a bit about myself and why you can trust me as a responsible and reliable host.

First off, I take great pride in providing clean and well-maintained vehicles for all my guests. Your comfort and safety are my top priorities, so you can expect a well-cared-for car.

I've been driving over 25 years and have a clean driving record. Safety is super important to me, so you can have peace of mind knowing that I'll take good care of you on the road.

If you have any questions or need assistance during your trip, don't hesitate to reach out. I'm here to help and make sure you have a smooth and enjoyable experience.

I'm also a big travel enthusiast, so if you need any recommendations or tips for your destination, feel free to ask. I love sharing my favorite spots and hidden gems!

Once again, thanks for choosing to rent with us. I'm excited to be your host and provide you with a fantastic Turo experience. 

Safe travels!

Thanks so much for looking at our vehicle options for your next trip! Melissa and I started Curated Luxury Auto, LLC in February of 2023 with 1 car. We had used Turo multiple times as guests but never dreamed we would become hosts. Fast forward to today and 18-20 cars on Turo and we have grown just a bit. We have grown because folks trusted us with their vehicle needs and we took that choice seriously. We try very hard to offer exceptional vehicles that match an exceptional experience all at an affordable price. Our experience and reputation has quickly made us the "go to" partner for luxury branded cars in the Indy market. We hope that we have the opportunity to show you what makes us different! We appreciate your support of our "Mom and Pop" business!

I’m Aurie, an All-Star host in the area with a small fleet of 3 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Feel free to check our reviews.

I look forward to being your host!

I’m traveling for work 50%. As I have a rental so often I’ve become determined to make a better experience for my guests than the larger companies can provide. I strive to offer you a cleaner, easier, more personalized trip. I’m located in Avon, and can pick you up from the airport if needed/available.
